                                    </div>
                                    <p class="has-medium-font-size">Biceps Long Head </p>
                                    <p class="has-small-font-size"><p>Most outside part of your bicep.The front of your upper arm.</p></p>
                                </div>
                                                            <div class="secondary-item muscle-item">
                                    <div class="muscle-img">
                                        <img src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Brachialis.png" alt="">
